ğŸ”¹ 1. Method in Java
ğŸ“˜ Definition:
    Method = Reusable block of code that performs some task.

        void sayHello() {
            System.out.println("Hello, bhai!");
        }
ğŸ§  Syntax:
    returnType methodName(parameters) {
        // logic
    }

    Example:
    int add(int a, int b) {
        return a + b;
    }

âœ… Why use com.samad.javacore.methods?
